---
title: Chicken Sausage & Lemon Spinach Ravioli with Bell Pepper & Parmesan
description: Craving a bit of sunshine? We’re right there with you. And while we can’t bring you perfect 80 degree weather, we can serve up a dish that’ll brighten your day. We’re talking tender pasta pillows stuffed with ricotta cheese and hearty spinach (already pretty awesome on their own), cloaked in a creamy, cheesy, lemon-spiked sauce. It’s gonna be a bright, bright, sunshiny meal!
